## CI Commands

```bash
cargo fmt --check
cargo clippy --workspace -- -D warnings
cargo test --workspace -- --test-threads=1
cargo doc --no-deps --workspace
```

No `source env.sh` required. No model downloads. All commands work offline.

Integration tests are automatically skipped when no Lemonade Server is reachable
(localhost probe finds nothing and `LEMONADE_URL` is unset). To **require** them
in CI, set `UFORGE_INTEGRATION_TESTS=require` — tests will panic instead of
silently skipping. To force-skip even when a server is present, set
`UFORGE_INTEGRATION_TESTS=skip`.

Always pass `--test-threads=1` — integration tests share GPU/NPU hardware on
the server and must not run concurrently.
